node.title: COVID-19: Auckland airport worker, household contact confirmed as Omicron cases
node.description: This is breaking news - more to come.
node.content: ["Genome sequencing has confirmed an Auckland Airport worker who tested positive for COVID-19 has the Omicron variant, the Ministry of Health said.\u00a0", "A household contact of the worker who tested positive on Tuesday also has the variant.\u00a0", "The Ministry of Health published a new location of interest relating to the case on Wednesday.\u00a0", "Anyone who was seated inside Ara-Tai Cafe at Half Moon Bay on January 18 from 12:30pm to 2:oopm is considered a close contact and must isolate and seek a test immediately and five days after the exposure.\u00a0", "This is breaking news - more to come.\u00a0", "\u00a0"]
